                        <lb n="2"/><seg real="++"><w lemma="τόσσος">τόσ<supplied reason="omitted">σ</supplied><unclear>ω</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ν</supplied></w></seg>
                        <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
